  <entry>
    <title>终端配置</title>
    <link href="/2026/05/08/%E7%BB%88%E7%AB%AF%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
    <url>/2026/05/08/%E7%BB%88%E7%AB%AF%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>终端：iterm2</p><p>zsh</p><p>oh-my-zsh</p><p><a href="https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/wiki/Themes">ohmyzsh主题下载地址</a></p><h1 id="把mac系统终端配置成ubuntu样式"><a href="#把mac系统终端配置成ubuntu样式" class="headerlink" title="把mac系统终端配置成ubuntu样式"></a>把mac系统终端配置成ubuntu样式</h1><p><strong>下载ubuntu字体</strong></p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">brew install --cask font-ubuntu-mono-nerd-font<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>在iterm2中设置字体</strong></p><p> iTerm2 里设置：iTerm2 → Settings → Profiles → Text → Font</p><p>选择字体UbuntuMono Nerd Font</p><p><strong>在zsh配置中修改样式</strong></p><p>进入zsh配置文件</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">vim ~/.zshrc<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置 <code>ZSH_THEME = &quot;&quot;</code></p><p>在最后一行添加</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">PROMPT=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;%F&#123;green&#125;%n@%m%f:%F&#123;blue&#125;%~%f$ &#x27;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>刷新</strong></p><p><code>source ~/.zshrc</code></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
    <tags>
      
      <tag>折腾</tag>
      
    </tags>
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>Git的使用</title>
    <link href="/2026/04/11/Git/"/>
    <url>/2026/04/11/Git/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="常用命令"><a href="#常用命令" class="headerlink" title="常用命令"></a>常用命令</h1><p>初始化git仓库<br>git init</p><p>git add .</p><p>git add 文件名</p><p>git commit -m “提交说明</p><p>git reset –hard</p><h1 id="commit规范"><a href="#commit规范" class="headerlink" title="commit规范"></a>commit规范</h1><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs nginx"><span class="hljs-attribute">git</span> commit -m <span class="hljs-string">&quot;类型: 做了什么&quot;</span> <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>常见类型：</p><figure class="highlight subunit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs subunit">feat: 新功能 <br>fix: 修 bug <br>docs: 文档 <br>style: 格式、样式调整，不影响逻辑 <br>refactor: 重构，不改变功能 <br><span class="hljs-keyword">test: </span>测试 <br>chore: 杂项，比如配置、依赖、构建脚本 <br>wip: 进行中的临时保存<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
    <tags>
      
      <tag>学习</tag>
      
    </tags>
    
